<section class="hero-wrapper">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-card animate-fade-in">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Conectividad Inteligente para empresas que no pueden detenerse</h1>
        <p>
          Internet dedicado, alta disponibilidad y seguridad empresarial con
          monitoreo 24/7/365. Diseñamos tu red para que tu operación siga
          corriendo, pase lo que pase
        </p>
        <div class="hero-btns">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Contactanos</a>
          <a href="#solutions" class="btn btn-outline">Soluciones</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-wrapper {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    padding-top: 100px;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .hero-card {
    height: 50vh;
    width: 120vh;
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background-color: #000829;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(0, 8, 41, 0.4), rgba(0, 8, 41, 0.4)),
      url("/hero-bg.png");
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    border-radius: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-card h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-card p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-btns {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-btns .btn {
    min-width: 160px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-card {
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      height: auto;
      min-height: 500px;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }
    .hero-card h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
